---
export interface Props {
  portfolio: { name: string; url: string; specialty: string; city: string }[];
}
const { portfolio } = Astro.props;
---
<section class="section-portfolio" id="portfolio">
  <div class="section-wrap">
    <div class="section-divider" style="margin-bottom:4rem"></div>
    <div class="portfolio-header">
      <span class="section-label">Portfólio</span>
      <h2>Profissionais que já transformaram sua presença digital</h2>
      <p>Sites estáticos, SEO real, presença nas IAs — todos no ar e indexados.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="portfolio-grid">
      {portfolio.map(p => (
        <a href={p.url} target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="portfolio-card">
          <div class="portfolio-avatar" aria-hidden="true">
            {p.name.split(' ').slice(0,2).map(w => w[0]).join('')}
          </div>
          <div class="portfolio-info">
            <h3>{p.name}</h3>
            <p class="portfolio-specialty">{p.specialty}</p>
            <p class="portfolio-city">📍 {p.city}</p>
          </div>
          <span class="portfolio-link">Ver site →</span>
        </a>
      ))}
    </div>
    <div class="portfolio-testimonial">
      <blockquote>
        "O serviço foi excelente desde o primeiro contato. O site saiu exatamente como pedi e, com a contribuição da equipe, ficou muito aderente ao meu nicho de trabalho. Todo o trabalho foi feito em colaboração comigo, num tempo recorde."
      </blockquote>
      <cite>— Dra. Ariane Pontes, Psicóloga Clínica — São Paulo/SP</cite>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .section-portfolio { padding: 5rem 0; }
  .portfolio-header { text-align: center; margin-bottom: 3rem; }
  .portfolio-header h2 { font-size: clamp(1.8rem,4vw,2.75rem); margin-bottom: 0.75rem; }
  .portfolio-header p { color: var(--brand-ink-muted); }
  .section-label {
    display: inline-block;
    font-family: var(--brand-font-body);
    font-size: 0.6875rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--brand-primary);
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
  }
  .portfolio-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(260px, 1fr));
    gap: 1rem;
    margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
  }
  .portfolio-card {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0.75rem;
    background: var(--brand-surface-alt);
    border: 1px solid var(--brand-border);
    border-radius: 0.75rem;
    padding: 1.25rem;
    text-decoration: none;
    transition: border-color 0.2s ease, transform 0.2s ease;
  }
  .portfolio-card:hover { border-color: var(--brand-primary); transform: translateY(-2px); }
  .portfolio-avatar {
    width: 2.5rem; height: 2.5rem;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #C8A44B, #D4B06A);
    color: #0B1D2E;
    display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
    font-family: var(--brand-font-body);
    font-size: 0.8125rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }
  .portfolio-info h3 { font-family: var(--brand-font-display); font-size: 1.0625rem; color: var(--brand-ink); margin-bottom: 0.25rem; }
  .portfolio-specialty { font-size: 0.875rem; color: var(--brand-ink-muted); margin: 0 0 0.25rem; }
  .portfolio-city { font-size: 0.8125rem; color: var(--brand-ink-faint); margin: 0; }
  .portfolio-link { font-size: 0.875rem; color: var(--brand-primary); font-weight: 500; margin-top: auto; }
  .portfolio-testimonial {
    max-width: 680px; margin: 0 auto;
    background: var(--brand-surface-alt);
    border-left: 3px solid var(--brand-primary);
    border-radius: 0 0.5rem 0.5rem 0;
    padding: 1.5rem 1.75rem;
  }
  .portfolio-testimonial blockquote {
    font-size: 1rem;
    color: var(--brand-ink);
    line-height: 1.7;
    font-style: italic;
    margin: 0 0 0.75rem;
  }
  .portfolio-testimonial cite {
    font-size: 0.875rem;
    color: var(--brand-ink-muted);
    font-style: normal;
  }
</style>
